title: Michael Angelo's Gourmet Foods, Inc. Recalls Shrimp Scampi and Meat Lasagna Products Due To Misbranding and Undeclared Allergens
summary: EDITORS NOTE: This release is being reissued as an expansion of the July 13, 2016 release to include additional products and production dates.
